<!-- ============================================
     NEXT MATCH / COUNTDOWN SECTION
     ============================================ -->
<section class="ts-countdown-section">
	<div class="ts-countdown-bg" style="background-image: url('https://playerstall.b-cdn.net/images/Surrey-Locker-Room.jpg"></div>
	<div class="ts-countdown-overlay"></div>
	<div class="ts-section-header light">
		<span class="ts-section-label">WHAT'S TRENDING</span>
		<h2 class="ts-section-title">GET YOUR CUSTOM LOCKER ROOM IN</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="ts-countdown-timer" id="countdown">
		<div class="ts-timer-block">
			<span class="ts-timer-number" id="countdown-days">00</span>
			<span class="ts-timer-label">DAY</span>
		</div>
		<div class="ts-timer-block">
			<span class="ts-timer-number" id="countdown-hours">00</span>
			<span class="ts-timer-label">HOUR</span>
		</div>
		<div class="ts-timer-block">
			<span class="ts-timer-number" id="countdown-mins">00</span>
			<span class="ts-timer-label">MINUTE</span>
		</div>
		<div class="ts-timer-block">
			<span class="ts-timer-number" id="countdown-secs">00</span>
			<span class="ts-timer-label">SECOND</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<a href="/contact" class="ts-match-cta">Get Started Today</a>
	<p class="ts-match-phone">Call us at <a href="tel:+18885841444" class="ts-match-phone-link">1 888 584 1444</a></p>
</section>

<section class="home-shop-section">
	<div class="home-shop-container">
		<!-- Materials We Use Section -->
		<div class="home-shop-section-header home-shop-section-header-spaced">
			<p class="home-shop-section-subtitle">THE LOCKER ROOM</p>
			<h2 class="home-shop-section-title">MATERIALS WE USE</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="ts-spotlight-inner-centered">
			<div class="ts-spotlight-content">
				<a href="/services" class="ts-spotlight-position">Premium Materials Collection</a>
				<div class="ts-spotlight-meta">
					<span>6-Layer Plywood</span> | <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="melamineLinkBtn" class="material-link">Melamine Finishes</a> | <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="woodGrainLinkBtn" class="material-link">Wood Grain</a> | <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="phenolicLinkBtn" class="material-link">Phenolic Options</a> | <span>ENF Certified</span> | <span>Fully Customizable</span>
				</div>
				<p class="ts-spotlight-bio">Built with premium 6-layer melamine-faced plywood featuring superior moisture resistance, termite protection, and fire-rated construction. Our proprietary layering process creates a core that's 40% stronger than standard plywood while meeting or exceeding all safety codes. Choose from an extensive range of melamine and laminate finishes including authentic woodgrain patterns, designer solid colors, and textured finishes. Each finish delivers exceptional durability and easy maintenance while maintaining the aesthetic appeal of natural wood. Also available in phenolic plastic for extreme durability in high-moisture locker room environments with 100% waterproof construction—perfect for pool areas, ice rinks, or any facility requiring maximum moisture resistance. All materials are ENF certified (zero harmful chemicals), water-resistant, and anti-fungal. Available in any dimension with your choice of finish, color, and hardware. Custom colors available upon request.</p>
				<div class="materials-buttons-container">
					<button id="viewAllColorsBtn" class="ts-btn ts-btn-filled">View All Colors</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================
     SERVICES / ACCORDION SECTION
     ============================================ -->
<section class="ts-services-section">
	<div class="ts-services-inner">
		<div class="ts-section-header">
			<span class="ts-section-label">OUR PROCESS</span>
			<h2 class="ts-section-title">HOW WE WORK WITH YOU</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="ts-services-tabs">
			<div class="ts-tab active" data-tab="0">
				<h4 class="ts-tab-title">Free Consultation</h4>
				<div class="ts-tab-content">
					<p>Every project starts with a free, no-obligation design consultation. Our team will work with you to understand your exact requirements, space constraints, and aesthetic preferences to deliver the perfect locker room solution.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ts-tab" data-tab="1">
				<h4 class="ts-tab-title">Custom Design</h4>
				<div class="ts-tab-content">
					<p>Choose from 6 locker models with fully customizable dimensions, wood species, finishes, and color options. From standard quick-ship models to fully bespoke installations, we build exactly what you need.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ts-tab" data-tab="2">
				<h4 class="ts-tab-title">Manufacturing</h4>
				<div class="ts-tab-content">
					<p>Our state-of-the-art manufacturing facility produces every locker with precision CNC cutting, hand-finished joinery, and multiple quality checkpoints. Quick ship in 2-4 weeks, custom in 8-12 weeks.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ts-tab" data-tab="3">
				<h4 class="ts-tab-title">Delivery & Install</h4>
				<div class="ts-tab-content">
					<p>We coordinate delivery nationwide and provide detailed installation guides. Our lockers are designed for easy assembly by your facilities team, with phone/video support always available.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

